main event: A UFO sighting was reported involving a cigar-shaped object observed in Elkton, Maryland on October 12, 1955.
interesting points: The object was estimated to be 125 feet in length,The cigar-shaped object was traveling south-east at 200 mph,The sighting lasted for about 10-15 minutes,There were aircraft known to be in the area at the time of the sighting,The report concluded the object probably was an aircraft due to insufficient data.
